content: I am staying at the Hilton Garden Inn Singapore and would like to travel to Changi Airport MRT station. I prefer not to use any mode of transport other than the MRT. Please design a route with the shortest walking distance. I remember that a friend is waiting for me at an MRT station along the way, where I need to meet her. Finally, please save all the stations passed in sequential order to a file named `routine.txt`, with one station per line.

I am unable to access the geocoding service to get precise coordinates for Hilton Garden Inn Singapore and Changi Airport MRT station. However, I can still help you plan the MRT route based on known MRT stations in Singapore.

To design a route from Hilton Garden Inn Singapore to Changi Airport MRT station using only MRT with the shortest walking distance, I need to know the nearest MRT station to Hilton Garden Inn Singapore and the MRT station where your friend is waiting.

Could you please provide the name of the MRT station closest to Hilton Garden Inn Singapore and the MRT station where your friend is waiting? This information will help me plan the route and save the stations passed in sequential order to the file "routine.txt."
